reference:
Imagick &Functions;
imagick




  &reftitle.intro;


   Imagick is a native php extension to create and modify images using the
   ImageMagick API.




  &reftitle.required;


   This extension requires ImageMagick version 6.2.4+ and PHP 5.1.3+.










  &reftitle.resources;


   Type of resource types (link id, etc.) this extension returns.

  &no.resource;


